 Read Bruce Tognazzini's article, &quot;<a href="http://www.asktog.com/columns/022DesignedToGiveFitts.html">A Quiz Designed to Give You Fitts</a>.&quot; There's a lot of interesting material at his <a href="http://www.asktog.com/index.html">asktog.com</a> site.</FONT></P>
<P><FONT FACE="AGaramond" SIZE=4>Look over the &quot;<a href="http://www.csc.ncsu.edu/faculty/healey/PP/index.html">Perception in Visualization</a>&quot; page by Christopher G. Healy. You don't have to read the entire text, but you should scan the examples and spend a few minutes playing with each of the two interactive demonstrations on the page.</FONT></P>
